Step: Search Firm History
Description: Search for similar projects in our firm's history using vector similarity search.

Input: {{ user_input }}

This step will:
1. Convert the project description into embeddings
2. Search the vector store (ChromaDB) for similar past projects
3. Return top matches with relevance scores
4. Extract learnings and recommended approaches from similar projects

The results will be available in the pipeline state as `search_firm_history`.
